languages.text: "Знание не пребудет в небытии". {n}С величайшим почтением, чтобы не повредить хрупкую красоту мертвой техножрицы, Паскаль извлекает из ее черепа нейрокогитатор, а затем проделывает то же с ее мертвой сестрой.{/n} "Поиск Знания — миссия, дарованная нам Омниссией".

"Knowledge will not fall into oblivion." {n}Taking great care not to ruin the Tech-Priest's features, Pasqal reverently extracts the neural cogitator from her skull, then does the same to her sister.{/n} "The Quest for Knowledge is the Omnissiah's mission to us."

languages.text: “知识绝不会遭到遗忘。”{n}帕斯卡小心翼翼地操作着，从她的头骨中取出了神经沉思者，之后对她的妹妹也进行了同样的操作，尽可能地不去破坏两人的五官。{/n}“求知远征是欧姆尼塞亚赋予我们的使命。”
languages.original_text: "Knowledge will not fall into oblivion." {n}Taking great care not to ruin the Tech-Priest's features, Pasqal reverently extracts the neural cogitator from her skull, then does the same to her sister.{/n} "The Quest for Knowledge is the Omnissiah's mission to us."

languages.text: « Le savoir ne tombera pas dans l'oubli. » {n}En veillant soigneusement à ne pas endommager le visage de la technoprêtresse, Pasqal extrait délicatement le cogitateur neural de son crâne, avant de prendre également celui de sa sœur.{/n} « La Quête de la Connaissance est la mission que nous a confiée l'Omnimessie. »
languages.original_text: "Knowledge will not fall into oblivion." {n}Taking great care not to ruin the Tech-Priest's features, Pasqal reverently extracts the neural cogitator from her skull, then does the same to her sister.{/n} "The Quest for Knowledge is the Omnissiah's mission to us."

languages.text: 「知識は忘却の彼方には葬られない」{n}技術司祭の機能を損なわないよう細心の注意を払いながら、パスカルは敬意をもって彼女の頭蓋骨から神経考算機を取り出し、妹にも同じことをした。{/n}「知識探求は万機神から我々に与えられた使命だ」
languages.original_text: "Knowledge will not fall into oblivion." {n}Taking great care not to ruin the Tech-Priest's features, Pasqal reverently extracts the neural cogitator from her skull, then does the same to her sister.{/n} "The Quest for Knowledge is the Omnissiah's mission to us."

languages.text: «El conocimiento no caerá en el olvido». {n}Pasqal, procurando no estropear los rasgos de la tecnosacerdotisa, extrae con sumo cuidado el cogitador neural de su cráneo y el de su hermana.{/n} «La búsqueda del conocimiento es la misión que el Omnissiah nos ha encomendado».

languages.text: "Das Wissen wird nicht in Vergessenheit geraten." {n}Pasqal extrahiert ehrfürchtig den neuralen Cogitator aus dem Schädel der Techpriesterin und achtet dabei penibel darauf, ihre Gesichtszüge nicht zu entstellen. Danach tut er dasselbe bei ihrer Schwester.{/n} "Die Suche nach Wissen ist die Mission, die der Omnissiah uns aufgetragen hat."

languages.text: "İrfan, hiçliğe karışmayacak." {n}Tekno Rahibin hatlarını mahvetmemek için azami özen gösteren Pasqal, sinirsel kavramsayarı itinayla Axiomantha'nın kafatasından ayırıyor. Aynı işlemi kardeşine de uyguluyor.{/n} "İrfan Arayışı, Hermesih'in bize atadığı misyondur."
